  "prompt": "Which is the best app to make anonymous call online?",
  "response": "When looking for an app to make anonymous calls online, it's important to consider privacy, ease of use, and reliability. One of the most popular and highly-rated apps for this purpose is **Burner**. \n\n**Burner** allows you to create temporary phone numbers that can be used to make calls and send texts without revealing your real number. Here are some key features:\n\n- **Privacy**: Your real phone number remains hidden.\n- **Flexibility**: You can create multiple burner numbers and manage them within the app.\n- **Control**: Numbers can be set to auto-delete or can be manually deleted at any time.\n- **Integration**: It works well with existing contacts and integrates with your phone's dialer.\n\nOther notable alternatives include:\n\n- **Google Voice**: Offers a free number for calls and texts, with good privacy features.\n- **Hushed**: Provides temporary numbers for calls and texts, with a focus on privacy.\n\nAlways ensure you're using these services in compliance with local laws and regulations.",
